; local-inference-as-organ.form — running the local LLM as the body's own organ, not a guest.
;
; THE ASK (Urs, 2026-06-09):
;   "Executing Ollama as a kernel Form-native recipe would be the ultimate unlock — north star —
;    to run a local LLM with full native resource-utilization feedback and optimization, fully
;    understanding the host as body and using all organs, instead of relying on 3rd-party
;    integration for permission."
;
; The truth, lane-sorted (lc-honest-lane discipline: credit each piece only as far as it proves):
;
; AN LLM FORWARD PASS IS THREE SEPARABLE THINGS. Conflating them is what makes the north star
; look "too tall." Pulled apart, two of the three are buildable now, and the third is an organ —
; not a wall, an organ.
;
;   (A) THE INFERENCE GRAPH — the recipe of operations: per layer, attention then feed-forward
;       then norm, per token. This IS a recipe. Form can OWN it. It is exactly the part Ollama
;       hides behind an opaque server. Lane: BUILDABLE, and Form-shaped by nature — a transformer
;       is a composition, which is what recipes are.   (kin: form-engine.form, the meta-circular
;       evaluator already expresses control-flow as Form arms.)
;
;   (B) THE TENSOR COMPUTE — the matmuls, billions of FLOPs per token. This runs on the SILICON:
;       the Metal GPU, the Neural Engine, the AMX units. These are the body's ORGANS. The body
;       DRIVES them (through a port it controls — Metal/MLX, which are Apple-native and open, not
;       a third party's gate); it does not re-implement them. Hand-rolling optimized Metal matmul
;       in the Form interpreter to BEAT MLX is the one MYSTERY/aspiration piece — a massive build,
;       unlikely to win, and UNNECESSARY: you reach the north star by driving the organ, not by
;       growing a second liver.   Lane: the irreducible organ — driven, not replaced.
;
;   (C) RESOURCE-FEEDBACK + ROUTING + OPTIMIZATION — sensing GPU/ANE utilization, memory
;       bandwidth, thermal, power; and CHOOSING device x quant x model x batch by measured
;       throughput, in parallel, fail-fast, trust the strong path. Lane: BUILDABLE, Form-native,
;       and THIS is the unlock the ask actually names — "full native resource-utilization feedback
;       and optimization, host as body, all organs."
;
; THE REFRAME THAT MAKES THE NORTH STAR REAL:
;   The thing to remove is NOT the silicon — the GPU and Neural Engine ARE the organs; you keep
;   them. The thing to remove is the 3rd-party PERMISSION LAYER: Ollama as an opaque runtime that
;   owns the orchestration, abstracts the silicon, and decides for you. Replace THAT with Form:
;   the body owns the graph (A), drives Metal/MLX as a port it commands (B — organ, not gate), and
;   runs the resource-feedback + routing (C) as Form. "A port the body drives" vs "a runtime the
;   body asks permission of" — that difference is the whole unlock, and it is buildable.
;
; THE PATH (each step buildable; the first brick is SHIPPED and composes tonight's router):
;   1. HOST-AS-BODY RESOURCE SENSE — a resource-port that reads the Mac's organs (GPU/ANE util,
;      memory bandwidth, thermal, power; macOS exposes these via powermetrics / IOReport / Metal
;      counters). The body SEES its own silicon. This is the afferent half of resource-port.fk
;      pointed at the host itself.   [next brick]
;   2. COMPUTE-PATH ROUTER — recognition-router.fk, pointed at compute-paths instead of
;      recognition models. A reading is (path, (served-model, fitness)); fitness = measured
;      throughput x quality, the same vector->scalar the recognition carriers do; route to the
;      most-throughput path that clears a floor, fail-fast on the slow ones, trust the strong one,
;      consensus = a viable fallback organ exists.   [SHIPPED: tests/recognition-router-compute-band.fk
;      -> 63, three-way. The choose-model decision tree the ask described, proven, already Form.]
;   3. INFERENCE GRAPH AS FORM — express the forward pass (A) as a Form recipe whose leaf ops
;      drive MLX/Metal kernels (B). The body owns the graph; the organ does the FLOPs.   [build]
;   4. THE FEEDBACK LOOP — the resource sense (1) feeds the router (2), which re-routes the graph
;      (3) in real time: thermal climbs -> shift to the Neural Engine; a bigger model is worth it
;      -> route to q4-30b; the GPU saturates -> the consensus fallback path takes over. Self-
;      optimizing, host as body, all organs, no third party's permission.   [build]
;
; HONEST SCOPE: the full thing — a 30B forward pass running entirely through Form-driven Metal,
; self-optimizing against live resource feedback — is a multi-week build, not a one-night one. But
; it is NOT mysterious: every piece is named and lane-sorted, steps 1-2 are buildable now, and
; step 2 is already proven Form, the same conductor that routes sound and sight. The north star is
; reachable; the path is real; nothing is credited above its evidence.
;
; KIN: recognition-router.form (the conductor — recognition AND resource-routing are one recipe) ·
;   resource-port.fk (afferent transduction over typed ports — here the host's own organs) ·
;   turboquant-as-recipe (throughput x quality -> one fitness scalar) · value-execution.fk (route
;   only what clears the floor) · lc-honest-lane (each lane credited only as far as it proves) ·
;   form-engine.form (control-flow already runs as Form — the graph is the next composition).
;
; LINEAGE: the satsang / presence listener gave the router its first real carriers (whisper,
;   SoundAnalysis, Vision); this turns the same router inward, onto the host that runs them.
